{
  "stem": "26672.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's a terrible thing to, uh, to have gone through a life and not remembering many things with them in childhood.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I used to be so jealous when I came across recent years of friends, say, oh, I've known them so long.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I've known them so long, and they did things together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I used to be terribly envious of them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And now, when I think of it, I also know people now that I've known 50 years, people I met up in the camps [INAUDIBLE] and since the camps, yeah.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So it's-- it's a long time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Yet, um, when you think about-- I was still-- I was envious.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were two very close friends of mine.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Whenever we got together, used to talk about holidays that you have to get together from school and the things they used to do in school.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I always used to think, if only I had someone who remembered me from home, yeah, what I was like.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My friends were here.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was one of my closest friends, Sidney Wagner.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He lives up the road here and David Halo.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "These are some of my closest friends, from English boys.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm talking about English bo-- boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Of course, many from my group that I know and--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The 458 Society, Holocaust survivors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We very close.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And also the boys that I've spent the time with in the different hostels since I've came to England or met [? up in ?] Theresienstadt or met up during the war-- my longest friend, another one is still alive.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's two actually.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One lives in Australia.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "His name is, um, Jack Feingold, Fein.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He calls himself Fein, used to be [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Feingzer, ?] calls himself Fein, that I visited uh, on a year ago in Australia.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
